{"tid":1666741,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有無鍾意整手工/畫畫的學生巴絲想一齊整野義賣，幫助發夢手足?","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T04:18:28.000Z","uid":101548,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2bbe731b522673ae5d45ae3d99be4a55ebc8539c","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"靈感來源係來自蕃茄師兄，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w83phdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw83phdW.png&h=fb3243f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個窮L和理非，成日見到有需要的眾籌都會好想幫手。<br />\n但如果係學生，本身都無咩錢，而我就係窮L，捐極有限，而自己又鍾意整手工，<br />\n見到蕃茄師兄POST覺得幾好，<br />\n想召募一班鍾意整手工/畫畫的學生巴絲想一齊整野義賣，<br />\n領去蕃茄師兄又得，領去OH YES!義賣群組又得，<br />\n甚至可能整得無咁靚，賣唔出時領去集會時派都得，<br />\n當為大家打氣。<br />\n我都係得初步概念，有興趣留言一齊傾，<br />\n之後再留TG開群組傾詳情。"},{"pid":"cb6ab4847dff1caa04441e01aaa75992145e9fe8","tid":1666741,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"354d6cb017d44de2f05bd995a481546ad28029c7","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"我見蕃茄師兄義賣的產品係整收縮膠/拼豆，<br />\n我畫畫寫字都好醜樣，但識整以上手工，<br />\n可以教有興趣的巴絲一齊整。<br />\n如果有畫畫/寫字靚的巴絲一齊整就更加好。<br />\n<br />\n或者可以整其他野都得?<br />\n有無巴絲有想法可隨便留言，<br />\n例如貼紙/明信片/滴膠/皮革。<br />\n我見義賣GROUP有整手足公仔，超靚，連我都想買返個。"},{"pid":"cc47edd3746f6187e4ec1b763a8201cb2ad5a6df","tid":1666741,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1986e3d3857557468f169a200d8f00bfb0e01de4","tid":1666741,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212e863a15640cce373c2545c50827f9821cda88","tid":1666741,"uid":195145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"我畫畫寫字都比人話過靚 你留tg傾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f7d168a6865d9811e55eb8731b6de2b7ea9f45","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1986e3d3857557468f169a200d8f00bfb0e01de4","tid":1666741,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打第一個留言，<br />\n絲打有無話識整D咩/畫畫叻呀?<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係食飯時碌FB見到，所以先膽粗粗開POST，<br />\n蕃茄師兄話佢D義賣產品好受歡迎，賣淨3個咋。<br />\n我估我地整完領去D黃店問下有無興趣做義賣，<br />\n唔知得唔得呢?例如龍門冰室咁，老闆好有型呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911ed0673862404f9953609d0177211d532f55a7","tid":1666741,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"縮膠一定最快<br />\noilpaint acrylic都可以<br />\nwatercolour要pick up翻原則上都得<br />\n可以試整3D嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我相信有market有人買<br />\n而我信縮膠鎖匙扣一定最快最平"},{"pid":"33eee8378f973e5eea4bc4eb8ee1c004df488a2d","tid":1666741,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"有art底但做開digital art 唔熟photoshop 所以冇幫手設計文宣 想喺art上面幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fa3e301955e7c91b8c6b146c68887810f3aa00","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"212e863a15640cce373c2545c50827f9821cda88","tid":1666741,"uid":195145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"我畫畫寫字都比人話過靚 你留tg傾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:41:40.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打，有無話想整d咩呀?<br />\n