1同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"d5d059631f4b9f78c1af7a2c36b3f4b68313fd8a","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"繼續推下post先，<br />\n初步諗住一個星期六早上一齊整，<br />\n等我研究下點開tg group先。"},{"pid":"cb48ca7e6b7e08b54dd15cb13bc75162a402538f","tid":1666741,"uid":215652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82179dfe1e7a13f01a6dc98937139251136a8b9d","tid":1666741,"uid":171838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:01:08.000Z","msg":"有興趣留名"},{"pid":"a15d7fb38f1b9443159689b7834037f0d229185e","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MBtdWBEwp6VMQYRzJTworA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMBtdWBEwp6VMQYRzJTworA&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=b7506908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MBtdWBEwp6VMQYRzJTworA</a><br />\n<br />\n開左tg group,有興趣參加的巴絲可入group"},{"pid":"64ce76ff0b7b57ce93afbeb7cffd035d3216b733","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb48ca7e6b7e08b54dd15cb13bc75162a402538f","tid":1666741,"uid":215652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7659b2618aada7ed5dfdf0611716302f219a0f","tid":1666741,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82179